          <span class="kicker">Conditions</span>
          <h1>Shoulder conditions we treat</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            We treat the full spectrum of shoulder pain, injury, and arthritis — with a focus on clear diagnosis,
            education, and a plan that fits your goals.
          </p>
