    <section class="section">
      <div class="container grid2">
        <div class="card pad">
          <h2>Rotator cuff</h2>
          <p class="muted">Tendinopathy, partial tears, full-thickness tears, traumatic tears, and chronic tears.</p>
          <div class="hr"></div>
          <ul>
            <li>Pain with lifting or reaching overhead</li>
            <li>Weakness, night pain, or loss of motion</li>
            <li>Non-surgical care vs repair discussion when appropriate</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card pad">
          <h2>Labrum & instability</h2>
          <p class="muted">Dislocations, recurrent instability, SLAP tears, Bankart lesions, and athlete shoulder.</p>
          <div class="hr"></div>
          <ul>
            <li>“Slipping” sensation or repeat dislocations</li>
            <li>Pain/catching with throwing or lifting</li>
            <li>Return-to-play planning and stabilization options</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card pad">
          <h2>Frozen shoulder</h2>
          <p class="muted">Adhesive capsulitis causing stiffness and pain with daily activities and sleep.</p>
          <div class="hr"></div>
          <ul>
            <li>Progressive loss of range of motion</li>
            <li>Night pain and difficulty reaching behind back</li>
            <li>Structured rehab + targeted interventions when indicated</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card pad">
          <h2>Arthritis</h2>
          <p class="muted">Glenohumeral arthritis, cuff tear arthropathy, and post-traumatic arthritis.</p>
          <div class="hr"></div>
          <ul>
            <li>Deep aching pain and stiffness</li>
            <li>Grinding or loss of function</li>
            <li>Non-surgical first; replacement consult when warranted</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card pad">
          <h2>Biceps / AC joint pain</h2>
          <p class="muted">Biceps tendinopathy, SLAP-related biceps pain, and AC joint arthritis/sprain.</p>
          <div class="hr"></div>
          <ul>
            <li>Front-of-shoulder pain with lifting</li>
            <li>Pain at top of shoulder with cross-body motion</li>
            <li>Activity-specific treatment planning</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="card pad">
          <h2>Second opinions</h2>
          <p class="muted">Review of imaging and prior treatment plans with straightforward recommendations.</p>
          <div class="hr"></div>
          <ul>
            <li>Clarify diagnosis and options</li>
            <li>Discuss timing and expectations</li>
            <li>Align plan with your goals and lifestyle</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
